thee; and goest thou thither again? Jesus answered, Are
there not twelve hours in the day? »If a man walk in the
day, he stumbleth not, because he seeth the light of this
world. But if a man walk in the night, he stumbleth, be-
cause the light is not in him. These things spake he: andTHE
