Then cometh Jesus with them unto a place called Geth-
semane, and saith unto his disciples, Sit ye here, while I go
yonder and pray. And he took with him Peter and the two
sons of Zebedee, and began to be sorrowful and sore troubled.
Then saith he unto them, My soul is exceeding sorrowful,
And
even unto death: abide ye here, and watch with me.
