I bessech you therefore, brethren, by the mercies of God,
to present your bodies a living sacrifice, holy, acceptable to
God, which is your spiritual service. And be not fashioned
according to this world: but be ye transformed by the re-
newing of your mind, that ye may prove what is the good
and acceptable and perfect will of God.
For I say, through the grace that was given me, to every
man that is among you, not to think of himself more highlyLETTERS
