judge him that eateth: for God hath received him. Who art
thou that judgest the servant of another? to his own lord he
standeth or falleth. Yea, he shall be made to stand; for the
Lord hath power to make him stand. One man esteemeth
one day above another: another esteemeth every day alike.
Let each man’ be fully assured in his own mind. He that
