churches shall
and hearts: and I will give unto each one of you according
to your works. But to you I say, to the rest that are in
Thyatira, as many as have not this teaching, who know not
the deep things of Satan, as they are wont to say; I cast
Nevertheless that, which ye
upon you none other burden.608
